Title: Webmaster
Actors: Lars Bom, Puk Scharbau, Jørgen Kiil, Karin Rørbeck
Plot: JB is the city's best attacker, who lives a carefully organized life in and outside the network. After hacking into the most powerful of all domains the Stoiser domain, JB thought that the cruel Stoiser would kill him. But instead he gave him a job - as a webmaster.
